OL,7,Fannounced his intention to step down
OL,8,Ffrom the role on Monday, after just
OL,9,Fover a year in office. His successor
OL,10,Fwill become Scotland's third since the
OL,11,Flast Holyrood election when they take
OL,12,Fpower.
OL,14,FThe comments from the hospitality
OL,15,Fgroup come as other business leaders
OL,16,Furged the next First Minister to make
OL,17,Feconomic growth a priority.
