OL,7,FDr Liz Cameron, chief executive of the
OL,8,FScottish Chambers of Commerce, urged
OL,9,Fthe new First Minister to "prioritise
OL,10,Feconomic growth" on Monday, whilst the
OL,11,FCBI said that "whoever comes in as
OL,12,FFirst Minister must put addressing
OL,13,FScotland's faltering economy first."
