OL,4,Cbusiness reacts as First Minster
OL,5,Cresigns
OL,7,FLast year Mr Yousaf said his programme
OL,8,Ffor government would be "pro-growth
OL,9,Fand anti-poverty," but he was
OL,10,Fcriticised by the Scottish
OL,11,FConservatives and Labour who felt he
OL,12,Fdidn't do enough to support small
OL,13,Fbusinesses in the last Scottish budget.
OL,15,FThe First Minister did not pass on the
OL,16,FUK Government 75% business rates
OL,17,Frelief for the hospitality sector and
OL,18,Fcreated a new 'higher rate' tax band
OL,19,Ffor those earning between #75,000 and
OL,20,F#125,000 a year.
