OL,7,F"With the new First Minister coming in
OL,8,Fthey need to have that complete reset
OL,9,Fwith business again.
OL,11,F"It'll be on the new First Minister to
OL,12,Feither look at the New Deal for
OL,13,FBusiness and say 'this is working or
OL,14,Fit isn't,' and then take it from there
OL,15,Fand start to reset that relationship
OL,16,Fyet again."
OL,18,FIn a statement a Scottish Government
OL,19,Fspokesperson said that the First
OL,20,FMinister was "proud to have laid the
OL,21,Ffoundations of his vision for Scotland.
